Package com.android.interfaces

Interface Manners<T extends Animal,​V extends Life>

All Known Implementing Classes:
Ape, Cappuchin, Chimp, Gorilla, Monkey, SpiderMonkey
public interface Manners<T extends Animal,​V extends Life>
T can be a Animal or one of the subclasses of Animal which are Elephant,Zebra,Cow. V can be a flower or a subclass of flower, Rose. both of these classes implement the Life interface. V can also be a anonymous class implementation of the Life Interface object. As Life is a Functional Interface, with only one abstract method, V can also be a Lambda
See Also:
Animal, Life
